name: Dizziness (JaminWang)
description:
A Cyberpunk Rhythm Combat Game Created with Gandi IDE

Join Discord server and create with us!

CAUTIONS: 

- If there is something wrong, please run the game again. Sorry for the bug. But it's not a long game, take it easy to restart.

- Please run the game again before you enter or quit the fullscreen.

- Turn FX on. The game will look better, but may cause laggy.

This game is created for Scratch Game Jam #1

Arts from Craftpix.net

Music by FabienC@RustedMusicStudio
